History file for DchCalib package
$Id: History 88 2010-01-14 12:32:57Z stroili $
======================================================================

14 Jan 10 - stroili
	split code in src and include directories

Tag V01-06-02

12 Aug 08 - gpdf
	Wrapped a frequent ErrMsg(debugging) in an ErrLogging test,
        in DchDedxCalib.cc.

Tag V01-06-01

21 Sep 07 - I. Gaponenko
	CLHEP migration: replaced forward declarations for CLHEP classes with
	direct includes of the corresponding header files. The modification
	is backward compatible with the old version of CLHEP.

Tag V01-06-00

10 Apr 07 - M. Kelsey
	DchBetheBloch.hh:  Merge separate ::ionization() signatures into
	  single "function" with TrkRecoTrk* as third argument, defaulting
	  to a null pointer.

	Requires rebuilding of all packages which depend on DchBetheBloch!

Tag V01-05-02

9 Apr 07 - M. Kelsey
	link_DchCalib.mk:  Fix dependences following changes below.

Tag V01-05-01

28 Mar 07 - M. Kelsey
	MAJOR BUG FIX:  DchBetheBloch functions were using momentum at IP
	for dE/dx computation, instead of momentum at DCH!

	DchBetheBloch.hh,cc:  Move DchPidInfo::getDchMomentum(TrkFit*) here
	  (static function).  This provides access to the function for all
	  of the DchCalibFcn/Dch*BB subclasses, so that they can correctly
	  use the DCH-volume momentum instead of the IP momentum when
	  computing expected dE/dx.

Tag V01-05-00 (M. Kelsey to restore numbering)

23 Oct 06 - P. Fisher
	- Modified routines to handle S. Telnov's track level calibration. 
	  Changed ionization(p,hpo) to ionization(TrkRecoTrk, hypo).

Tag V01-03-02 for 16.0.3 and beyond
Tag V01-02-07 for 16.0.2x builds

[ Note, previously recorded tags burned to add second debugging message. ]

23 Feb 05 - M. Kelsey
	- DchDedxCalib.cc:  Add debugging message to ::calibrateCharge()
	  and to constructor.

Tag V01-02-05

28 Oct 04 - S. Gowdy
	- DchDedxCalibList.cc: Update #if to avoid potential warning.

Tag V01-02-04

28 Oct 04 - S. Gowdy
	- DchTimeToDistList.hh: remove unused includes.
	- DchDedxCalibList.cc: Add workaround for Sun CC <=5.4 problem.

Tag V01-01-05

08 May 04 - M. Kelsey
	- DchTimeToDistList.cc:  Remove assert()'s from getTimeToDist.

Tag V01-00-07

10 Apr 03 - G. Raven (by M. Kelsey)
	- Add direct access to dE/dx global gain factor

12 Mar 03 - M. Kelsey
	- remove RW dependency

04 Sep 01 - M. van Hoek
        - added base class for smearing of MC tdc times (a la MC efficiencies)

10 Aug 01 - M. van Hoek
        - update of DchMCEff.hh to encorporate MC efficiencies as fct of charge.

12 Jun 00 - R. Stroili
	- fix a memory leak in DchWireStatusList

02 Feb 00 - R. Stroili
	- move BetheBloch, BetheBlochErr concrete classes and factories 
	  to DchCalibFcn package

28 Jan 00 - M. Kelsey
	- updated link_DchCalib.mk to current source code dependencies.

11 Jan 00 - R. Stroili
	- remove classes DchQSatMasa & DchQSatCorrFactory (now they're in 
	  DchCalibFcn)

10 Jan 00 - J. Roy
          - Added a new resolution function (DchBBCoupalErr)
          - Combine all calibration functions into a single one
            with the class DchCalibFcn/DchDedxCorrFun.
          - Moved the charge saturation functions to DchCalibFcn
            along with DchQSatCorrFactory to decouple DchCalib from
            changes in calibration functions.

08 Oct 99 - R. Stroili
	- fix bug in DchQSatMasa -> the correction was the reverse....
	  (always use multiplicative terms....)

04 Oct 99 - R. Stroili
	- Remove hardcoded saturation corrections
	- add classes for charge saturation corrections:
		- DchQSatCorr: abstract class
		- DchQSatMasa: implementation of Masa-Coupal parametrization
		- DchQSatCorrFactory: factory

Aug 26 1999- G.Sciolla
        - Add charge as a parameter to several functions in DchCalib.hh/cc
        - DchDedxDipAngle25Fun.cc: new saturation corrections. 
          WARNING: new parameters are hardcoded: bad bad bad. Change it soon! 

18 Aug 99 - G.Sciolla 
        Add DchGlobalGasGain.hh/cc to store the global run by run gas gain in 
	DB

25 Jul 99 - R. Stroili
	Add a method to DchBetheBlochFactory to return a default 
	parametrization (Dch5ParBB)

12 Jul 99 - R. Stroili
	Add parametrization for Bethe-Bloch resolution: at the moment 
	introduced an abstract class for interface definition, a concrete class
	that implements a constant flat resolution and a factory used to 
	create a concrete object from a data file or an array or values

03 Jul 99 - R. Stroili
	put back Bill changes

03 Jul 99 - R. Stroili
	DchBetheBloch is now an abstract class. Added two concrete classes
	(Dch5ParBB, a 5 parameter B-B, and DchPidParBB, a 10 parameter
	B-B with possibility of PID-dependent scalings)

29 Jun 99 - R. Stroili  (part 2)
	put back changes from Bill

29 Jun 99 - R. Stroili
	Fix a check in DchBetheBloch constructor ...........

27 Jun 99 - R. Stroili  (part 2)
	put back changes from Bill

27 Jun 99 - R. Stroili
	DchBetheBloch extended to 5 parameters. It's backward compatible,
	it will work also with a database giving 4 parameters only, the fifth
	one (the exponent to beta at the denominator) will be set to 2. There's
	no change to the function itself
  
03 Jun 99 - F.Wilson (FFW-990603)
        DchDedx*Fun.cc rewritten. No longer typedefs but subclasses that
        add a DefaultValues() method to initialise the functions to a known
        state (i.e. gain corrections and functions are all 1.0)
        Changes needed to be coordinated with DchProxy and DchCond (FFW-990603)

03 Jun 99x - F.Wilson FFW-990602
       Tag head so can rollback if necessary
07 Apr 99 - F. Wilson (FFW-990407)
        Added gainCorrection() to DchDedxCalib. Needed by DchData/DchdEdx.

31 Mar 99 - R. Stroili
	fix problem in DchBetheBloch (when reading file), replaced char* 
	with RWCString

23 Mar 99 - F. Faleazzi R. Stroili
	added Bethe-Bloch function for PID reconstruction

15 Mar 99 - F.Wilson (FFW-150399)
         - allow inverse to be used outside its domain (DchGenericInverse)
        
13 Mar 99 - F.Wilson (FFW-130399)
         - Pruned the interface to DchDedxCalib
         - Added Pid info as possible calibration variable to DchdexCalib
           interface.
         - Put in divide by zero checks on correction functions

10-MAR-99 - F.Wilson (FFW-100399)
Addition of routines DchDedx*.{cc,hh} for applying dE/dx calibrations.
Also required changes in DchOpr, DchEnv, DchCond and DchProxy with the above
tag.

20 June 1998 - R. Faccini
	Add functionalities to make Non linear fits in calibration.
	Make the TtoD class inherit from CalSpectrumG and be steered by a CalParmMgr
	Old functionalities left
       
18 May 1998 -	R. Stroili
	added an abstract class |DchAbsTimeToDistance| and a derived one
	to start moving away from non-OO DchDriftCalib class

20 Jan 1998 -	R. Stroili
	changed GNUmakefile to work with incremental link

08 Nov 1997 -	R. Stroili
	first use of this package. Moved DchDriftCalib and DchReadCalConst
	from DchData to remove circular dependency
